README & INSTRUCTION

|- How to Run?

$ java -jar Tic.jar

|- Tic

In Game Screen, play tic-tac-toe. The rule can be referred from the internet :)
Besides clicking on the screen the perform a "drawing", key press of 1 through 9 can also have 
the same effect.

In Prompt Screen, it prompts you who is the winner or if there is a draw. Use the mouse to click
on any place in the screen can restart/start a new game.

We put a time limit on each player's turn. If the player does not make a move when the time
expires, it becomes the other player's turn and the timer resets.

|- Tac


